# Runtime-mutated NPC state — MEMORY.md files are rewritten every tick by the
# NPC brains. Keeping them out of VCS avoids huge noisy diffs on every run.
# SOUL.md files stay tracked (they define the NPC's personality).
npcs/*/MEMORY.md

